evidence.text: ORDER granting 51 Letter Motion for Leave to File Document. The Court is in receipt of Defendants letter dated June 16, 2025 seeking leave to file a Supplemental Declaration and Notice of Supplemental Authority in further support of their Opposition to Plaintiffs Motion for a Preliminary Injunction (Dkt. No. 51). Defendants request is hereby GRANTED. Plaintiffs should be prepared to discuss their response to Defendants letter (Dkt. No. 51), if any, at tomorrows hearing. (Entered: 06/16/2025)

evidence.text: ORDER granting 61 Letter Motion for Extension of Time. Defendants' extension request is hereby GRANTED. The Parties may each file a letter with the Court, no later than 5:00 p.m., by July 11, 2025. The letter may not exceed three pages and shall comply with this Court's Individual Practices. SO ORDERED. (Signed by Judge Andrew L. Carter, Jr on 6/30/25) (yv) (Entered: 06/30/2025)
